Okay, so I've been asked to find the new administrative unit for "Xã Hòa Phong, Huyện Tây Hoà, Tỉnh Phú Yên". First, I need to understand that "Tỉnh Phú Yên" merged with "Tỉnh Đắk Lắk" and the new province name is "Tỉnh Đắk Lắk" according to Resolution 60-NQ/TW.

Now, focusing on the specific address "Xã Hòa Phong, Huyện Tây Hoà", I need to find the new ward within "Tỉnh Đắk Lắk". My process involves meticulously searching through resolutions, specifically those related to administrative changes within "Tỉnh Đắk Lắk".
